-- Shares in Turkey's Tekstilbank surge 9 percent after ICBC deal
-- 
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 08:15AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, April 29 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Tekstilbank <TEKST.IS> jumped 8.84 percent to 1.6 lira on Tuesday after Industrial and Commercial Bank of China Ltd <1398.HK> said it had agreed to buy a 75.5 percent stake in the bank for $316 million.

